{"tid":1074653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(屯門人) 屯門跌左八達通","createTime":"2019-03-23T14:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T14:05:04.000Z","uid":193226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bb835ebc51f5383aae95759f6ad3a1f5b6141f92","tid":1074653,"uid":193226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"岩岩係屯門巴紐睇完戲返，屋企上車前發現跌左八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n23/3/2019 係巴紐睇左場1院 1930分開既戲<br />\n走個時完場大約係 9點到 行左去Vcity牛角對出個廁所<br />\n之後行去屯西506站想上車 點知發覺唔見左八達通 <br />\n<br />\n八達通由個淺藍色八達通套入住<br />\n八達通係個人八達通黎<br />\n面有張即影即有相<br />\n後面個格仲有一張個人相<br />\n如果有人係拾到既話 麻煩你留私一私信我<br />\n張相對我好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}